These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-1::.
There are 2 different favourite colors: ivory, ebony
2 different pets are kept: goat, turtle
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: cycling, surfing
The people use 2 different means of transport: jet-ski, taxi
1. the person driving the taxi is on the left or right of the person who's sport is surfing##3
2. the person who likes ebony is in an even position##4
3. the owner of the turtle is the person who likes ivory##1
4. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |
| Color      | ivory  | ebony   |
| Pet   | turtle     | goat   |
| Sport         | surfing | cycling |
| Transport     | jet-ski | taxi    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-2::.
There 2 different types of food: avocado, cabbage
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, documentary
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, azalea
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: vegafina, siglo
1. the person who growsazalea is in an odd position##4
2. the person watching action movies is the siglo-smoker##1
3. the person eating cabbage is on the right of the person watching documentary movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |
| Food          | avocado     | cabbage |
| Movie-Genre   | documentary | action  |
| Flower           | azalea         | aconite     |
| Cigar     | vegafina   | siglo    |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-3::.
House: craftsman, cottage
The people have 2 different jobs:  accountant, entrepreneur
2 different pets are kept: frog, lizard
The people grow 2 different varities of flowers: aconite, sunflower
1. the person who growssunflower is on the left or right of the entrepreneur##3
2. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the entrepreneur##1
3. the craftsman house is in an even position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |
| House    | cottage     | craftsman |
| Job         | entrepreneur | accountant    |
| Pet         | frog         | lizard        |
| Flower   | aconite         | sunflower    |

