.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-4-20::.
The people prefer 2 different music-genres: gospel, pop
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, doctor
2 different pets are kept: frog, goat
The people have 2 different hobbies: filmmaking, video-games
1. the doctor is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
2. the owner of the frog is on the left or right of the fan of pop##3
3. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is in an odd position##4

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |    2     |
| Music-Genre    | gospel | pop    |
| Job         | doctor        | designer |
| Pet         | frog          | goat     |
| Hobby   | filmmaking        | video-games     |

 